{"tid":1323938,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［強身健體］零經驗健身絲打請入～","createTime":"2019-07-16T12:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T07:17:56.000Z","uid":261095,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b048eee4baeb080c57e79739ca71ff5cc0e51a55","tid":1323938,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"對應返我上一個post，有啲野我想再詳細講，專for未做過無氧運動或者對運動無咩認識嘅絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">1. 每日+運動前後拉筋</span></span><br />\n目的：柔軟度提高，防止拉傷<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dk0Neb96tCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdk0Neb96tCo&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTefroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=7cee310d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dk0Neb96tCo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">2. 體脂率高（25%^）</span></span><br />\n體脂高嘅絲打除左做無氧，可以配合埋有氧消脂，另外HIIT同時有增肌燃脂作用，想成效快啲，需要配合飲食，<span style=\"color: violet;\">「七分飲食，三分運動」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n最快方法係「生銅飲食」，即係完全戒澱粉質。實行兩個月就應該見成效。如果無法完全戒澱粉，可以選擇其中一、兩餐拒食澱粉，或者<span style=\"color: violet;\">減少澱粉質</span>份量。唔需要節食，照食肉類同蔬菜，得閒飲下綠茶都有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n澱粉質例如粥粉麵飯、麵包等等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">3. 唔夠力點算？</span></span><br />\n一般女仔上肢較弱，做唔到掌上壓，可以由<span style=\"color: violet;\">牆上壓</span>開始練，記得做肌肉訓練個時保持呼吸，<em><strong>用力呼，放鬆吸</strong></em>，除左掌上壓，有其他動作都可以鍛練手臂。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YXCjEtDKIpA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYXCjEtDKIpA&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTefroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=636c7a09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YXCjEtDKIpA</a><br />\n呢條片適合<em>弱雞&middot;無力&middot;零經驗新手</em>，當你做到覺得無難度，可以再加強訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">4. 無時間運動</span></span><br />\n我唔信你一日入面抽唔到15分鐘出黎，15分鐘都可以做到HIIT，而且上個po 同呢個po 我share嘅片絕對係屋企都做到，器材都唔洗，唔好話攰又盛，唔好俾藉口自己，而且我相信<span style=\"color: blue;\">宜家呢個時勢你仲懶落去嘅話，咁我幫你唔到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bleOTMDa3_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbleOTMDa3_4&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTefroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=69a76ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bleOTMDa3_4</a>"},{"pid":"145818a2bd77ed441dce202b212e8d5afe71f940","tid":1323938,"uid":132287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:18:57.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n無論咩事都好 做多d運動一定對你人生有幫助"},{"pid":"3803c45b700061d0800c53e396278f3f435acf40","tid":1323938,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d9b2d962833ba0f135cf6012d05c8a55fc4cefc","tid":1323938,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15b8801846f17f203ac8bcfac5b403b6041cd11b","tid":1323938,"uid":221968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175b131a8ee7adb789777e0c4c23fef912a31886","tid":1323938,"uid":221968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:00:37.000Z","msg":"Coffee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c97b6f11d56e60010d2532a2e6c929304067cc8","tid":1323938,"uid":221968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:02:45.000Z","msg":"Btw 絲打 ， 生酮飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee3890a3eb03e01109b2888834c9bfeed1a2317","tid":1323938,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c97b6f11d56e60010d2532a2e6c929304067cc8","tid":1323938,"uid":221968,"like":0,"